# Metric Agent (Go) - Starter

Small system metrics collector that exposes:
- /metrics (JSON snapshot)
- /metrics-prom (Prometheus metrics)
- /healthz

## Build & run
go mod tidy
go run ./cmd/agent -listen :9100 -interval 5s

## Docker
docker build -t metric-agent .
docker run -p 9100:9100 metric-agent

## Tests
go test ./... -v
